# **Vintage Classic Barber Shop** Color Rules

## Core Color Palette
```css
/* Vintage Classic Palette */
--primary-brown: #8B4513;      /* Saddle Brown - main brand color */
--accent-gold: #D4AF37;        /* Gold - premium accents */
--neutral-beige: #F5F5DC;      /* Beige - soft backgrounds */
--text-dark: #2F2F2F;          /* Dark Gray - primary text */
--text-light: #6B4423;         /* Medium Brown - secondary text */
--background: #FAFAFA;         /* Off-White - main background */
--cream: #FFF8DC;              /* Cornsilk - subtle sections */
--dark-brown: #654321;         /* Dark Brown - deep accents */
```

## Color Distribution Rules

### **60-30-10 Rule Application:**
- **60% Neutral Base**: Off-white (#FAFAFA) and beige (#F5F5DC) backgrounds
- **30% Primary Brown**: Saddle brown (#8B4513) for headers, navigation, key sections
- **10% Gold Accents**: Gold (#D4AF37) for buttons, highlights, premium elements

## Element-Specific Color Rules

### **Header & Navigation:**
```css
Background: #8B4513 (Saddle Brown)
Text: #FAFAFA (Off-White)
Logo accent: #D4AF37 (Gold)
Active nav item: #D4AF37 (Gold) background
Hover effect: #654321 (Dark Brown)
```

### **Call-to-Action Buttons:**
```css
Primary CTA: #D4AF37 (Gold) background, #2F2F2F (Dark) text
Secondary CTA: #8B4513 (Brown) outline, #8B4513 (Brown) text
Hover Primary: #B8860B (Darker Gold)
Hover Secondary: #8B4513 (Brown) background, #FAFAFA (Off-White) text
```

### **Content Sections:**
```css
Main background: #FAFAFA (Off-White)
Card/Panel background: #F5F5DC (Beige)
Alternate sections: #FFF8DC (Cream)
Borders: #D4AF37 (Gold) - 1px solid
Dividers: #C4A484 (Muted Gold)
```

### **Typography Colors:**
```css
Headlines (H1-H2): #2F2F2F (Dark Gray)
Body text: #2F2F2F (Dark Gray)
Secondary text: #6B4423 (Medium Brown)
Links: #8B4513 (Saddle Brown)
Link hover: #D4AF37 (Gold)
Captions/metadata: #8B7355 (Light Brown)
```

## Vintage-Specific Design Rules

### **Decorative Elements:**
- **Gold borders**: Use #D4AF37 for premium service highlights
- **Brown dividers**: #8B4513 for section separators
- **Subtle shadows**: rgba(43, 67, 35, 0.1) for depth
- **Vintage patterns**: Use beige (#F5F5DC) backgrounds with subtle textures

### **Service Cards/Pricing:**
```css
Card background: #F5F5DC (Beige)
Card border: 2px solid #D4AF37 (Gold)
Service title: #2F2F2F (Dark Gray)
Price: #D4AF37 (Gold) - larger, bold
Description: #6B4423 (Medium Brown)
```

### **Form Elements:**
```css
Input background: #FAFAFA (Off-White)
Input border: #8B4513 (Brown)
Input focus: #D4AF37 (Gold) border
Label text: #2F2F2F (Dark Gray)
Placeholder: #8B7355 (Light Brown)
```

## Semantic Color Applications

### **Status Indicators:**
```css
Success: #8B4513 (Brown) - keeping vintage theme
Warning: #CD853F (Peru Brown) - vintage-friendly orange
Error: #A0522D (Sienna) - muted red-brown
Info: #6B4423 (Medium Brown)
```

### **Interactive States:**
```css
Default button: #D4AF37 (Gold)
Hover: #B8860B (Dark Gold)
Active: #8B4513 (Brown)
Disabled: #C4A484 (Muted Gold) with 50% opacity
```

## Accessibility Rules

### **Contrast Requirements Met:**
- Dark Gray (#2F2F2F) on Off-White (#FAFAFA): 12.6:1 ✓
- Brown (#8B4513) on Beige (#F5F5DC): 4.8:1 ✓
- Gold (#D4AF37) on Brown (#8B4513): 4.1:1 ✓
- White text on Brown background: 8.9:1 ✓

## Usage Guidelines

### **Do's:**
- Use gold sparingly for premium elements
- Maintain warm, earthy feeling throughout
- Layer different browns for depth
- Use beige/cream for soft section breaks

### **Don'ts:**
- Avoid bright, modern colors (neon, electric blue)
- Don't use pure black - stick to dark grays/browns
- Avoid high contrast combinations outside the palette
- Don't overuse gold - keep it special

### **Vintage Texture Suggestions:**
- Subtle paper texture on beige backgrounds
- Leather texture hints on brown elements
- Aged/weathered effects on borders
- Classic serif fonts to complement colors

This vintage classic palette creates a **warm, traditional, and premium** feeling perfect for established barbershops with heritage and craftsmanship focus.


